{"tid":2092033,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"今晚CCTVB偽人袁偉豪有活動","createTime":"2020-07-03T04:07:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T08:47:52.000Z","uid":17646,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b93bbd67e9bdd1c4370432ea05c18055c46ba82d","tid":2092033,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T04:07:37.000Z","msg":"大家去支持下佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1721826975.rsc.cdn77.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/09143739/0_20206417166.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1721826975.rsc.cdn77.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2F09143739%2F0_20206417166.jpg&h=88c82e9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼鐵探之後，袁偉豪、惠英紅同黑仔又再次同台演出啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好開心，明知警察響市民心目中形象咁差，TVB既警匪膠劇仲係無日無之，無線真係有好多科幻劇編劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">係咪覺得比我呃咗入黎好嬲呢？嬲就岩啦，拉落去派嬲thanks，有時間順便聽晚七點去朗豪坊，問吓佢有無興趣轉電視台</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gosREyc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgosREyc.jpg&h=9cdcb789&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【每日任務@02 Jul】<br />\n💎SABON X 袁偉豪💎<br />\n「快樂地享受當下」...原來SABON搵咗TVB偽人袁偉豪代言，仲要明晚7點鐘喺朗豪坊有新店開張！咁又真係幾快樂嘅，聽晚偽人仲會親臨新店添！<br />\n<br />\n不如我地今晚做個前奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SabonHK/posts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSabonHK%2Fposts&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=9a47bc99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SabonHK/posts</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sabonhk/?hl=zh-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsabonhk%2F%3Fhl%3Dzh-hk&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=ffe6ebdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/sabonhk/?hl=zh-hk</a><br />\n<br />\n順手勸下袁偉豪棄暗投明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BenjaminYuenJBH/posts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBenjaminYuenJBH%2Fposts&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=604ca156\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/BenjaminYuenJBH/posts</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/benontheroad/?hl=zh-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbenontheroad%2F%3Fhl%3Dzh-hk&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=fedac8da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/benontheroad/?hl=zh-hk</a> </div><br />\n<br />\n最後，大家聽日收工後有一個好去處，歡迎大家相約親朋戚友同去慶賀，令到SABON更「快樂地享受當下」：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">日期：7月3日（五）<br />\n時間：晚上7時<br />\n地點：旺角朗豪坊B1地庫13號舖</span></span><br />\n<br />\nSayno4tvb小編呼籲：請大家在留言、新店現場保持和理非，不要做恐嚇等事......<br />\n<br />\n1.如果你唔認同佢地既營商手法，請入facebook比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.如果你想佢地改過，請留言回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.如果你真係唔鍾意佢地，咁就唔好再買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.對志同道合既手足留言比個讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民間TVB團隊</span>需要大家既支持</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno4tvb%2F&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=d25c5e49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb/</a><br />\nTG: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno4tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno4tvb&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=e45d11a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno4tvb</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NbYiswE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNbYiswE.jpg&h=d3b9ed92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5opp9mv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5opp9mv.jpg&h=dad5157b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CaC3Fta.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCaC3Fta.png&h=12416031&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dVG4nk5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdVG4nk5.jpg&h=69dd4c04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"316ff8abc08d2c0c6f81dda04d12aed1e1b0e931","tid":2092033,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T04:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0c4096679a62139c0936ae81462469cf402ca0","tid":2092033,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T04:13:40.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"e1ee577244bef03975790fa3353f251b370d222e","tid":2092033,"uid":127425,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T04:13:56.000Z","msg":"期待黑仔同紅姐<br />\n幾時做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac74c4a568c82ce2c505aa70f16cf0e9fde5d8f8","tid":2092033,"uid":84668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T04:21:29.000Z","msg":"PISH  今晚見"},{"pid":"714de43bd6e90cf6c988828addaa1b0f99997779","tid":2092033,"uid":24457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T04:23:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee8b1ed71016faa5d1fb21ae15123e2403aec96","tid":2092033,"uid":51924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply